title: 3 and Out - Russ Cooked, Week 5 Preview and 3 for the $$ Picks
itunes:title: 3 and Out - Russ Cooked, Week 5 Preview and 3 for the $$ Picks
description:
John reacts to Russell Wilson’s awful TNF performance in a disappointing home loss to the Colts, and if the Broncos are already a sinking ship. He also dives into the Tom Brady/Gisele divorce rumors, the mixed bag of NFL results for recent Lincoln Riley QB’s, and Steelers fans coming back to earth in the post-Big Ben era.

Then, he runs 3 Week 5 NFL games by Action Network sharp Stuckey to see if there's professional agreement or disagreement on this week’s picks! 

Subscribe NOW and follow Middlekauff and The Volume on Twitter, Instagram and YouTube for the latest content. It's always FanDuel for the best wagering action! #volume #herd
